  <other_name type="common_name">Bolander's quillwort</other_name>
  <discussion>Small plants with leaves less than 2.5 cm have been called Isoëtes bolanderi var. pygmaea (Engelmann) Clute.</discussion>
  <discussion>Isoëtes bolanderi hybridizes with I. echinospora and I. occidentalis.</discussion>
